query.sfwSql: SELECT * FROM SGT_MAILING_lABEL ML ORDER BY RUN_DATE DESC
SELECT * FROM SGT_MAILING_LABEL_PERSON_TYPE MLPT WHERE ML.MAILING_LABEL_BATCH_ID=MLPT.MAILING_LABEL_BATCH_ID
SELECT * FROM SGT_MAILING_LABEL ML WHERE RUN_DATE IS NULL AND OUTPUT_FORMAT_VALUE='FILE'
SELECT DISTINCT COUNTY FROM SGT_COUNTY_REF
SELECT PA.PERSON_ID AS PERSON_ID FROM SGT_PERSON_ACCOUNT PA WITH (NOLOCK) INNER JOIN SGT_PERSON PER WITH (NOLOCK) ON PER.PERSON_ID=PA.PERSON_ID AND PER.DATE_OF_DEATH IS NULL
SELECT PA.PERSON_ID AS PERSON_ID FROM SGT_PERSON_ACCOUNT PA WITH (NOLOCK) INNER JOIN SGT_PERSON PER WITH (NOLOCK) ON PER.PERSON_ID=PA.PERSON_ID AND PER.DATE_OF_DEATH IS NULL

SELECT ISNULL(BENEFICIARY_PERSON_ID,0) AS PERSON_ID FROM SGT_PERSON_BENEFICIARY BENE WITH (NOLOCK) LEFT JOIN SGT_PERSON PER WITH (NOLOCK) ON PER.PERSON_ID=BENE.BENEFICIARY_PERSON_ID AND PER.DATE_OF_DEATH IS NULL

SELECT BENE.BENEFICIARY_PERSON_ID AS PERSON_ID FROM SGT_PERSON_BENEFICIARY BENE WITH (NOLOCK) INNER JOIN SGT_PERSON PER WITH (NOLOCK) ON PER.PERSON_ID=BENE.BENEFICIARY_PERSON_ID AND PER.DATE_OF_DEATH IS NULL INNER JOIN SGT_PERSON_ACCOUNT_BENEFICIARY SPAB WITH (NOLOCK) ON SPAB.BENEFICIARY_ID=BENE.BENEFICIARY_ID INNER JOIN SGT_PERSON_ACCOUNT SPA WITH (NOLOCK) ON SPA.PERSON_ACCOUNT_ID=SPAB.PERSON_ACCOUNT_ID

SELECT ISNULL(DEP.DEPENDENT_PERSLINK_ID,0) AS PERSON_ID FROM SGT_PERSON_DEPENDENT DEP WITH (NOLOCK) LEFT JOIN SGT_PERSON PER WITH (NOLOCK) ON PER.PERSON_ID=DEP.DEPENDENT_PERSLINK_ID AND PER.DATE_OF_DEATH IS NULL GROUP BY DEP.DEPENDENT_PERSLINK_ID

SELECT DEP.DEPENDENT_PERSLINK_ID AS PERSON_ID FROM SGT_PERSON_DEPENDENT DEP WITH (NOLOCK) INNER JOIN SGT_PERSON PER WITH (NOLOCK) ON PER.PERSON_ID=DEP.DEPENDENT_PERSLINK_ID AND PER.DATE_OF_DEATH IS NULL INNER JOIN SGT_PERSON_ACCOUNT_DEPENDENT SPAD WITH (NOLOCK) ON SPAD.PERSON_DEPENDENT_ID=DEP.PERSON_DEPENDENT_ID INNER JOIN SGT_PERSON_ACCOUNT SPA WITH (NOLOCK) ON SPA.PERSON_ACCOUNT_ID=SPAD.PERSON_ACCOUNT_ID

SELECT PC.CONTACT_PERSON_ID AS PERSON_ID FROM SGT_PERSON_CONTACT PC WITH (NOLOCK) INNER JOIN SGT_PERSON PER WITH (NOLOCK) ON PER.PERSON_ID=PC.CONTACT_PERSON_ID AND PER.DATE_OF_DEATH IS NULL WHERE RELATIONSHIP_VALUE='SPOU' AND STATUS_VALUE='ACT'
SELECT CITY FROM SGT_COUNTY_REF WHERE COUNTY=@COUNTY

SELECT PER.PERSON_ID FROM SGT_PERSON PER INNER JOIN SGT_PERSON_EMPLOYMENT EMP ON PER.PERSON_ID=EMP.PERSON_ID INNER JOIN SGT_PERSON_EMPLOYMENT_DETAIL DTL ON DTL.PERSON_EMPLOYMENT_ID=EMP.PERSON_EMPLOYMENT_ID
SELECT COUNT(*) FROM SGT_ORG_PLAN WHERE PLAN_ID=@PLANID AND ORG_ID=@ORG_ID

SELECT * FROM SGT_ORGANIZATION WHERE ORG_ID IN (SELECT ORG_ID FROM SGT_ORG_CONTACT WHERE ORG_CONTACT_ID IN(SELECT ORG_CONTACT_ID FROM SGT_ORG_CONTACT_ROLE WHERE CONTACT_ROLE_VALUE=@CONTACT_ROLE)) AND STATUS_VALUE='ACTV'

SELECT PER.LAST_NAME + ',' + PER.FIRST_NAME AS lstrFullName, PERS.ADDR_LINE_1 AS lstrAddressLine1, PERS.ADDR_LINE_2 AS lstrAddressLine2, PERS.ADDR_CITY AS lstrCity, CV.DESCRIPTION AS lstrState, CTY.COUNTY AS lstrCountry, PERS.ADDR_ZIP_CODE AS lstrZipCode, PER.PERSON_ID AS lintID FROM SGT_PERSON PER WITH (NOLOCK) INNER JOIN SGT_PERSON_ADDRESS PERS WITH (NOLOCK) ON PER.PERSON_ID=PERS.PERSON_ID INNER JOIN SGT_COUNTY_REF CTY ON LOWER(CTY.CITY)=LOWER(PERS.ADDR_CITY) INNER JOIN SGS_CODE_VALUE CV ON PERS.ADDR_STATE_VALUE=CV.CODE_VALUE AND CV.CODE_ID=150 WHERE PER.PERSON_ID=@PERSON_ID

SELECT ORG.ORG_NAME AS lstrFullName, ORGCON.ADDR_LINE_1 AS lstrAddressLine1, ORGCON.ADDR_LINE_2 AS lstrAddressLine2, ORGCON.CITY AS lstrCity, CV.DESCRIPTION AS lstrState, ORGCON.ZIP_CODE AS lstrZipCode, CTY.COUNTY AS lstrCountry, ORG.ORG_ID AS lintID FROM SGT_ORGANIZATION ORG INNER JOIN SGT_ORG_CONTACT_ADDRESS ORGCON ON ORGCON.ORG_ID=ORG.ORG_ID INNER JOIN SGT_COUNTY_REF CTY ON LOWER(CTY.CITY)=LOWER(ORGCON.CITY) INNER JOIN SGS_CODE_VALUE CV ON ORGCON.STATE_VALUE=CV.CODE_VALUE AND CV.CODE_ID=150 WHERE ORG.ORG_ID=@ORG_ID AND ORG.STATUS_VALUE='ACTV'

SELECT * FROM SGT_ORGANIZATION WHERE STATUS_VALUE='ACTV' AND (((ORG_TYPE_VALUE=@ORG_TYPE_VALUE) AND (@ORG_TYPE_VALUE <> '')) OR (@ORG_TYPE_VALUE ='')) AND (((EMP_CATEGORY_VALUE=@EMPL_TYPE_VALUE) AND (@EMPL_TYPE_VALUE <> '')) OR (@EMPL_TYPE_VALUE =''))
SELECT * FROM SGT_ORG_CONTACT WHERE ORG_ID=@ORG_ID AND STATUS_VALUE='ACTV' ORDER BY CREATED_DATE ASC
SELECT COUNT(*) FROM SGT_MAILING_LABEL WHERE [FILE_NAME] = @FILE_NAME
SELECT SPA.PERSON_ID FROM SGT_PERSON_ACCOUNT SPA INNER JOIN SGS_CODE_VALUE CV ON CV.CODE_ID=SPA.PLAN_PARTICIPATION_STATUS_ID AND SPA.PLAN_PARTICIPATION_STATUS_VALUE=CV.CODE_VALUE

select distinct SPA.payee_perslink_id from sgt_payee_account SPA WITH (NOLOCK) inner join SGT_PERSON P WITH (NOLOCK) on P.person_id = SPA.Payee_perslink_id AND P.DATE_OF_DEATH IS NULL where account_relation_value = 'ALTP'

select distinct spa.payee_perslink_id from sgt_payee_account SPA WITH (NOLOCK) inner join SGT_PERSON P WITH (NOLOCK) on P.person_id = SPA.Payee_perslink_id AND P.DATE_OF_DEATH IS NULL where account_relation_value = 'MEMB'
select SPA.person_id from sgt_person_account SPA with (nolock) inner join SGT_PERSON P WITH (NOLOCK) on P.person_id = SPA.person_id where plan_participation_status_value = 'RTRD'

select distinct SPA.payee_perslink_id from sgt_person_account PERA WITH (NOLOCK) inner join SGT_PERSON P WITH (NOLOCK) on P.person_id = PERA.person_id AND P.DATE_OF_DEATH IS NULL inner join sgt_payee_account SPA WITH (NOLOCK) on PERA.person_id =SPA.Payee_perslink_id and account_relation_value = 'MEMB' and plan_participation_status_value = 'RTRD'

select distinct SPA.payee_perslink_id from sgt_person_account PERA WITH (NOLOCK) inner join SGT_PERSON P WITH (NOLOCK) on P.person_id = PERA.person_id AND P.DATE_OF_DEATH IS NULL inner join sgt_payee_account SPA WITH (NOLOCK) on PERA.person_id =SPA.Payee_perslink_id and account_relation_value = 'MEMB'

select distinct SPA.payee_perslink_id from sgt_person_account PERA WITH (NOLOCK) inner join SGT_PERSON P WITH (NOLOCK) on P.person_id = PERA.person_id AND P.DATE_OF_DEATH IS NULL inner join sgt_payee_account SPA WITH (NOLOCK) on PERA.person_id =SPA.Payee_perslink_id and account_relation_value = 'ALTP'
